{
  "id": "L16",
  "title": "Returning a Faulty Product",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "In this lesson, you'll learn how to return a faulty item to a store ('le magasin'). Let's start with how to approach a staff member."
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E01",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Bonjour",
        "meaning": "Hello"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E02",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Excusez-moi",
        "meaning": "Excuse me"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L16_V01",
      "data": {
        "Le produit": "The product"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E03",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "J'ai une question",
        "meaning": "I have a question"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L16_V02",
      "data": {
        "La machine à café": "The coffee machine"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E04",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "J'ai acheté",
        "meaning": "I bought"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "pronunciation",
      "item_id": "L16_P01",
      "data": {
        "word": "acheté",
        "phonetic": "/aʃ.te/",
        "tip": "The 'h' is silent and the final 'é' sounds like 'ay' in 'say'."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L16_V03",
      "data": {
        "Ici": "Here"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L16_V04",
      "data": {
        "La semaine dernière": "Last week"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L16_V05",
      "data": {
        "Cassé / Cassée": "Broken"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "French adjectives change based on gender. Use 'cassé' for masculine nouns ('le produit') and 'cassée' for feminine nouns ('la machine')."
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E05",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "D'accord",
        "meaning": "Okay / Alright"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L16_S01",
      "title": "Explaining the Problem",
      "setting": "You are in an electronics store and need to return a broken coffee machine.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "title": "Get the staff member's attention and say you have a question.",
          "chatbot_message": "Bonjour."
        },
        {
          "title": "Explain that you bought the coffee machine here last week.",
          "chatbot_message": "Oui ?"
        },
        {
          "title": "State that the coffee machine is broken.",
          "chatbot_message": "D'accord. Le problème ?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "Great start! Now, you need to show your proof of purchase and suggest what you'd like to do next."
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L16_V06",
      "data": {
        "Le ticket de caisse": "The receipt"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E06",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "S'il vous plaît",
        "meaning": "Please"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E07",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Voici",
        "meaning": "Here is..."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E08",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Merci",
        "meaning": "Thank you"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "`Je voudrais...` is a very useful and polite way to say 'I would like...'."
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E09",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Je voudrais",
        "meaning": "I would like"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L16_V07",
      "data": {
        "Une nouvelle": "A new one (feminine)"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L16_V08",
      "data": {
        "Ou": "Or"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L16_V09",
      "data": {
        "Un remboursement": "A refund"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L16_V10",
      "data": {
        "Un moment": "One moment"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L16_S02",
      "title": "Proposing a Solution",
      "setting": "The conversation continues. The staff member is waiting for you to suggest a solution.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "title": "Show the receipt.",
          "chatbot_message": "D'accord. Le ticket de caisse, s'il vous plaît."
        },
        {
          "title": "Say you would like a new one.",
          "chatbot_message": "Merci."
        },
        {
          "title": "Alternatively, ask for a refund.",
          "chatbot_message": "D'accord."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "Excellent! Let's finish the conversation. You'll need to agree to their solution and thank them."
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E10",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Parfait",
        "meaning": "Perfect"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "pronunciation",
      "item_id": "L16_P02",
      "data": {
        "word": "Parfait",
        "phonetic": "/paʁ.fɛ/",
        "tip": "The final 't' is silent."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E11",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "C'est bon",
        "meaning": "That's good / That's fine"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E12",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Merci beaucoup",
        "meaning": "Thank you very much"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E13",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Pour votre aide",
        "meaning": "For your help"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E14",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Bonne journée",
        "meaning": "Have a good day"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L16_S03",
      "title": "Finalizing the Return",
      "setting": "The staff member has returned and is offering you a solution.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "title": "Agree to the offer of a new machine.",
          "chatbot_message": "D'accord. Un moment... Voilà. Une nouvelle machine pour vous."
        },
        {
          "title": "Confirm that everything is sorted out.",
          "chatbot_message": "Parfait."
        },
        {
          "title": "Thank the staff member for their help.",
          "chatbot_message": "C'est bon. Bonne journée !"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}